    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.21-25_0001"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">21</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    Albany Ore
                
                    <salute>Dear friend John: -</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Its been a long time since Ive heard from you or seen you.</p>
                
                <p>Im staying with my sister Edna, in Albany Ore.</p>
                
                <p>My wife passed away in August of last year. We had been married 55 years and its kinda tough.</p>
                
                <p>I have a sister-in-law and brother-in-law that lives here too.</p>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.21-25_0002"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">22</fw>
                
                <p>I would like to see you sometime. If you ever come out this way let me know</p>
                
                <p>We have two of your books out of the library "Black Elk Speaks" and "When the Tree Flowered"</p>
                
                <p>I haven't done any work a couple of years.</p>
                
                <p>Time drags. I dont do any thing. I dont know what to do.</p>
                
                <p>I did live in Los Angeles. A Man there by the name of William Olson that went to the Nebraska
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.2.21-25_0003"/>
                    
                    Normal when we did. I use to see him often.</p>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">23</fw>
                
                <p>Do you remember the time we went from Kansas City to Waverly, Missouri to saw timber? We got thrown in jail.</p>
                
                <p>I want to hear from you &#8212; please write soon. Will write more next time.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely</salute>
                    <signed>John E. Chaffee</signed>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>c/o Edna Skillings</addrLine>
                        <addrLine><hi rend="caps">K. P.</hi> apt #4</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Albany Ore.</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </closer>
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26.21-25_0004"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">24</fw>
                
            </div1>
            
            
